\par\pard\plain \fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He stood up. The great bulk of him dwarfed Mandrameen. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandrameen\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s knees almost buckled. }
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Salavan pounced.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hold still, Mandrameen! Hold still!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Stop! Help!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Salavan used his great strength to wrestle Mandrameen\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s flailing limbs into submission, and used his weight to squeeze the air from Mandrameen\u8217\'92s lungs. He delighted in the pitiful sound that Mandrameen made as he wheezed. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 If you are the true artist bidden by Asharaheen, then we will see eachother again, and I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ll apologize for this. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Tears streamed down Mandrameen\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s face and his lungs burned in agony. Salavan paused his ramblings to delight in the picture. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93There\u8217\'92s no greater feeling,\u8221\'94 he muttered.}
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93EAAAUUUGHHH!\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandrameen was dead.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Potential composition.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 As a final composition it was a busy piece.}
